## 七、Checkpoint 设计

```sql
-- engine/checkpoint.py 管理的 SQLite 表

CREATE TABLE checkpoints (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    stage TEXT NOT NULL,         -- architect | developer | critic | complete
    state JSON NOT NULL,         -- 完整状态快照
    created_at TIMESTAMP,
    parent_id TEXT REFERENCES checkpoints(id)
);

CREATE TABLE task_results (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    checkpoint_id TEXT REFERENCES checkpoints(id),
    agent_type TEXT NOT NULL,    -- architect | developer | critic
    batch_num INTEGER,
    output JSON NOT NULL,        -- Agent 输出
    gate_results JSON,           -- 闸门检查结果
    commit_hash TEXT,            -- git commit
    test_summary JSON,           -- 测试结果摘要
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);
```

**中断恢复流程**：

```python
def resume(checkpoint_id: str) -> DevLoopResult:
    checkpoint = Checkpoint.load(checkpoint_id)
    loop = DevLoop(graph=..., gates=..., runtime=...)
    loop.checkpoint = checkpoint     # 注入恢复状态
    loop.step = checkpoint.step + 1
    return loop.continue_from(checkpoint)
```

